code: @Override @After public void tearDown() throws Exception {     if (clientConnector != null) {         try {             clientConnector.close().         } catch (Exception e) {         // ignore         }         clientConnector = null.     }     super.tearDown(). }

@Override protected MBeanServerConnection getMBeanConnection() throws Exception {     if (mbsc == null) {         if (clientConnector == null) {             clientConnector = JMXConnectorFactory.connect(new JMXServiceURL(jmxServiceUrl), null).         }         mbsc = clientConnector.getMBeanServerConnection().     }     return mbsc. }
